    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_1827-1855",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1827-1855",
      "markText": "消灭自身对“功绩”的观念，因为它对精神是一种莫大的障碍。",
      "totalCount": 195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1827&rangeEnd=1855",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1827&rangeEnd=1855"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_1920-1956",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1920-1956",
      "markText": "一切选择是可怕的，当你考虑选择的时候：可怕的是一种不复为义务所及的自由。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1920&rangeEnd=1956",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1920&rangeEnd=1956"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_6_881-919",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "881-919",
      "markText": "愿我这书能教你对自己比对它感兴趣——而对自己以外的一切又比对你自己更感兴趣。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=881&rangeEnd=919",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=881&rangeEnd=919"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_2521-2576",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2521-2576",
      "markText": "让重要性在你自己的目光中，而并非在所看到的事物上。",
      "totalCount": 135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2521&rangeEnd=2576",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2521&rangeEnd=2576"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_5_1571-1603",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1571-1603",
      "markText": "能教你对自己比对它感兴趣，而对自己以外的一切又比对你自己更感兴趣",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1571&rangeEnd=1603",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1571&rangeEnd=1603"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_13181-13237",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "13181-13237",
      "markText": "在书本中读到海滩上的沙土是轻柔的，这对我是不够的；我愿我赤裸的双足印在上面……任何未经感觉的认识对我都是无用的。",
      "totalCount": 110,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=13181&rangeEnd=13237",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=13181&rangeEnd=13237"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_803-871",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "803-871",
      "markText": "我懒散的、长期昏睡的幸福醒来了……",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=803&rangeEnd=871",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=803&rangeEnd=871"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_2713-2779",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2713-2779",
      "markText": "欲望是有益的，同样，有益的是欲望的满足——因为欲望从而增添。我实在对你说，奈带奈蔼，每种欲望比我欲望中的目的物虚幻的占有更使我充实。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2713&rangeEnd=2779",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2713&rangeEnd=2779"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_6758-6807",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "6758-6807",
      "markText": "什么突然来到的东西还能不是从我们自身所产生的呢？而什么我们所可能的东西还不早已是我们所知道了的呢？",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6758&rangeEnd=6807",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6758&rangeEnd=6807"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_8_3163-3252",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3163-3252",
      "markText": "明日的梦是一种快乐，但明日的快乐又是另一种快乐，可喜没有事物能与自己所梦想的正相符合；因为每一事物的价值在于互不相似。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3163&rangeEnd=3252",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3163&rangeEnd=3252"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_4_2818-2852",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2818-2852",
      "markText": "纪德始终认为只有使自己的灵魂永不松弛，永不祈求安息，人才能永远年轻。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2818&rangeEnd=2852",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2818&rangeEnd=2852"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_3228-3249",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3228-3249",
      "markText": "宁过一种至情的生活，奈带奈蔼，而不求安息。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3228&rangeEnd=3249",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3228&rangeEnd=3249"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_5417-5515",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5417-5515",
      "markText": "而我们的生命在我们面前将似这满装冰水的杯子，这执在发烧的病人手上湿润的杯子，他渴，他竟一饮而尽，他明知道他应静待，但他无法从他的唇边推开这甘美的杯子。水是那样沁凉，而发烧的热度却又那样地使他枯焦。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5417&rangeEnd=5515",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5417&rangeEnd=5515"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_10192-10209",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "10192-10209",
      "markText": "智者即是对一切事物都发生惊奇的人。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10192&rangeEnd=10209",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10192&rangeEnd=10209"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_8_2237-2303",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2237-2303",
      "markText": "鹰心醉于高翔。夏夜使莺沉醉。原野因酷热而战栗。奈带奈蔼，让一切情绪对你变成一种陶醉。如果你所吃的不曾使你心醉，那因为你并不十分饥饿。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2237&rangeEnd=2303",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2237&rangeEnd=2303"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_1527-1573",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1527-1573",
      "markText": "当别人正从事发表或工作，我却过了三年旅行生活，为的，相反地，忘去一切我曾藉头脑所学得的事物。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1527&rangeEnd=1573",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1527&rangeEnd=1573"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_2976-3062",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2976-3062",
      "markText": "由此我在自身中达到排斥同情的境地，因为在同情中所见到的只是一种共通情绪的认识。不需要同情，奈带奈蔼——而是爱。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2976&rangeEnd=3062",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2976&rangeEnd=3062"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_1422-1435",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1422-1435",
      "markText": "万物都指神，无一能启示神。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1422&rangeEnd=1435",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1422&rangeEnd=1435"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300079401_7_4124-4135",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "4124-4135",
      "markText": "忧郁只是消沉后的热诚。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300079401&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4124&rangeEnd=4135",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/07632b70813ab8584g011170?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4124&rangeEnd=4135"
